data.token-verwenden#Token verwenden:
Fügen Sie das Token in jeden API-Request als Bearer-Token im Authorization-Header ein:
curl https://app.logistikapp.ch/api/v1/materials \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer IHR_TOKEN_HIER" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
// JavaScript / Node.js
const response = await fetch('https://app.logistikapp.ch/api/v1/materials', {
  headers: {
    'Authorization': `Bearer ${process.env.LOGISTIKAPP_TOKEN}`,
    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
  }
});
const data = await response.json();
# Python
import requests
headers = {
    'Authorization': f'Bearer {os.environ["LOGISTIKAPP_TOKEN"]}',
    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
}
response = requests.get('https://app.logistikapp.ch/api/v1/materials', headers=headers)

